Per VW Tech bulletin 10-90 no head gaskets are to be used. I have not
lapped any heads I have installed and have had no problems.

Overheating can be caused by just plain pushing your bus too hard. If
you suspect vacuum leaks, consider the manifold gasket, and the
manifold sleeves at the plenum.

